      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 load configuration (compression-bending at 5 mm/min displacement rate). Only one test condition evaluated; the COU encompasses quasi-static loading only, which limits the breadth of condition coverage. This factor is below the required level 3; identified as a gap in the credibility assessment. Achieved level 2 does not meet required level 3.",
