      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance for pedicle screw mechanical performance. Each QoI directly informs the regulatory decision regarding structural adequacy of the implant. QoIs are measurable in both FEA output and physical test. Achieved level 3."
